<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Saihnuna</author>
<hymn_number>191</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel hi pawtsan leng, kinunghei ta lo-in;
 Kipaka chiehsa te'n,
 Pielgal gam nuom ah ei ngak ui,
 Kumsawt nawpna a chun.

[V2]
 Kah leh lungkhamna gam,
 Khawvel ka chenna hi;
 Lungguolna Zion tang chungah,
 I lenkal ka ngaklah.

[V3]
 2. Entie, Lalpa ka len- nau gam lungkhamna hi;
 Gamgaw dahum a hi,
 Thihna'n guolngaih ei khen zing sek,
 Na gam tun ma hin chu.

[V4]
 3. Lalmang Immanuel, khawpi Zion achun;
 Kikhenna a um puoi,
 Ziechun lungkham, liengvai chate,
 Kituok khawm ka ngaklah.</lyrics>
<title>Lungguolna Zion Tang</title>
</song>